==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Surprising
<hw>Sur*pris"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Exciting surprise;
extraordinary; of a nature to excite wonder and astonishment; <as>as,
<ex>surprising</ex> bravery; a <ex>surprising</ex> escape from
danger.</as></def> -- <wordforms><wf>Sur*pris"ing*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Sur*pris"ing*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Wonderful; extraordinary; unexpected;
astonishing; striking.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

